{"title":"Samba服务配置.md","uid":"06198761e580b0e02e2f2ad4b32ad7e9","slug":"Samba服务配置-md","date":"2022-07-21T05:09:06.000Z","updated":"2022-07-21T05:15:07.435Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/Samba服务配置-md.json","keywords":null,"cover":null,"content":"<link rel=\"stylesheet\" class=\"aplayer-secondary-style-marker\" href=\"\\assets\\css\\APlayer.min.css\"><script src=\"\\assets\\js\\APlayer.min.js\" class=\"aplayer-secondary-script-marker\"></script><pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">安装所需软件包：\nyum install –y samba samba-client\nsystemctl restart smb</code></pre>\n\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">编写配置文件：\nvim &#x2F;etc&#x2F;samba&#x2F;smb.conf</code></pre>\n\n<h2 id=\"基本参数\"><a href=\"#基本参数\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"基本参数\"></a>基本参数</h2><table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>map to guest&#x3D;bad user</th>\n<th>实现无密码访问</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody><tr>\n<td>comment</td>\n<td>描述该共享的名称</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>path</td>\n<td>定义该共享的目录</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>browseable</td>\n<td>指定共享的目录是否可浏览</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>writable</td>\n<td>指定共享的目录是否有写入权限</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>readonly</td>\n<td>指定共享的目录为只读权限</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>write list&#x3D;</td>\n<td>指定哪些用户可以在该只读共享文件上有写的权限</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>public</td>\n<td>指定是否可以允许Guest帐户访问</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>guest ok</td>\n<td>通public相同，yes为允许guest访问</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>onlyguest</td>\n<td>指定只有guest用户可以访问</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>valid users</td>\n<td>指定访问该共享的用户</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>createmask&#x3D;</td>\n<td>创建文件的权限</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>directorymask&#x3D;</td>\n<td>创建目录的权限</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>forceuser&#x3D;</td>\n<td>指定创建文件的默认属主</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>veto files &#x3D;&#x2F;<em>.exe&#x2F;</em>.com&#x2F;*.dll&#x2F;</td>\n<td>限制上传某文件类型</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>veto files &#x3D;&#x2F;<em>root</em>.*&#x2F;</td>\n<td>限制关键字</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>admin users &#x3D; hardy</td>\n<td>samba的管理用户，默认是root</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Null  password &#x3D; yes</td>\n<td>是否允许空密码</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>invalid  users &#x3D; root</td>\n<td>不可登陆用户</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>max connections &#x3D; 0</td>\n<td>最大连接数</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>hide dot files &#x3D; yes</td>\n<td>是否隐藏点文件</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>hide files &#x3D; &#x2F;<em>.java&#x2F;</em>.cpp&#x2F;</td>\n<td>隐藏指定文件</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table>\n<h2 id=\"给samba用户设置密码\"><a href=\"#给samba用户设置密码\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"给samba用户设置密码\"></a>给samba用户设置密码</h2><pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">useradd user1 \nsmbpasswd  –a user1         </code></pre>\n\n\n\n\n\n","feature":true,"text":"安装所需软件包： yum install –y samba samba-client systemctl restart smb 编写配置文件： vim &#x2F;etc&#x2F;samba&#x2F;smb.conf 基本参数 map to guest&#x3D;bad u...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":928,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"Centos","slug":"Centos","count":7,"path":"api/categories/Centos.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"Centos","slug":"Centos","count":6,"path":"api/tags/Centos.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%9F%BA%E6%9C%AC%E5%8F%82%E6%95%B0\"><span class=\"toc-text\">基本参数</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E7%BB%99samba%E7%94%A8%E6%88%B7%E8%AE%BE%E7%BD%AE%E5%AF%86%E7%A0%81\"><span class=\"toc-text\">给samba用户设置密码</span></a></li></ol>","author":{"name":"H-MiKing","slug":"h-miking","avatar":"https://s2.loli.net/2022/03/09/hnWbjs6yMGKDXdk.jpg","link":"/","description":"新手博客，在校大学生，曾获得某省技能大赛一等奖。","socials":{"github":"https://github.com/H-MiKing","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"https://www.zhihu.com/people/hjsuo","csdn":"https://blog.csdn.net/weixin_51369125?spm=1000.2115.3001.5343","juejin":"","customs":{"bilibili":{"icon":"/svg/bilibili.svg","link":"https://space.bilibili.com/346448962?spm_id_from=333.1007.0.0"}}}},"mapped":true,